                  <author n="3">Budge, E. A. W.</author>
                  <title n="3">The Book of Paradise, being the Histories and Sayings of the Monks and Ascetics of the Egyptian Desert by Palladius, Hieronymus and others (Lady Meux Manuscript, 6) 2</title>
                  <citedRange n="3">p. 192-198 (syr.)</citedRange>
               </bibl>
            </note>
